TestTool.Model.TestCreation

Class BasicTestCreation

  • java.lang.Object
    • TestTool.Model.TestCreation.BasicTestCreation

  • public abstract class BasicTestCreation
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores the settings needed to create a basic test. Also contains the function to create a test.
